headline: 1 Crucial Factor Driving This 5.3%-Yielding Dividend Stock's Unstoppable Growth
summary: Vici Properties (NYSE: VICI) has grown significantly over the years.  When it formed in 2017, the real estate investment trust (REIT) owned 20 casino properties leased to several different gaming operators.  Today, it owns a diversified portfolio of 93 experiential real estate assets leased to 13 gaming and entertainment tenants.
